text: Saah Nyumah (born 2 July 1997) is a Liberian footballer who plays for LISCR, as a midfielder. ==Career== Born in Vonjama, Nyumah has played for Red Lions, Wassaman United and LISCR. He made his international debut for Liberia in 2015. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Liberian footballers Category:Liberia international footballers Category:Red Lions FC (Liberia) players Category:Emmanuel Stars F.C. players Category:LISCR FC players Category:Association football midfielders Category:Liberian expatriate footballers Category:Liberian expatriate sportspeople in Ghana Category:Expatriate footballers in Ghana
